es to unanimously out-score Talash and advance to the competition proper.\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2130, \"end\": 2135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.9844696167479863, \"rank\": 0.0132000711357559, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2143, \"end\": 2148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.8994578253888026, \"rank\": 0.11068810526914445, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my thing\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2057}, {\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2080}, {\"ngram\": \"the first breaker\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2169}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic stage\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2190}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2214}, {\"ngram\": \"power moves\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2229}, {\"ngram\": \"to unanimously out-score Talash\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am super-happy to be here, and I am proud to be the first one,\\\" said India, the 2022 world champion.\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2375, \"end\": 2380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.8994578253888026, \"rank\": 0.11068810526914445, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2022 world champion\", \"from\": 2382, \"to